## Configuration

### JWT Configuration

Dans `config/auth.php` :

```php
'defaults' => [
    'guard' => 'api',
    'passwords' => 'users',
],

'guards' => [
    'api' => [
        'driver' => 'jwt',
        'provider' => 'users',
    ],
],
```

### CORS (optionnel)

Si vous utilisez un frontend séparé, configurez CORS dans `config/cors.php` :

```php
'paths' => ['api/*'],
'allowed_methods' => ['*'],
'allowed_origins' => ['*'],
'allowed_headers' => ['*'],
```

